<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1113076">Achieve sexual release, either alone or with a partner, and then defile a page torn from the religious canon of a lawful good deity. Gain a +4 bonus on saves against enchantment effects.<br>遵从仪式：<del>与一位或多位伴侣</del>一起达到性高潮，然后玷污一页从守序善良神明的教典上撕下来的书页。在对抗惑控系<del>法术</del>时豁免获得+4加值。<br>是独自或跟一位伴侣<br>对抗惑控系效果<br><br>Mind-affecting spells you cast that would normally grant an additional saving throw or a bonus on saving throws for opposing the target’s nature do not grant these bonuses or saves<br>这句是指支配人类中「当受术者被迫进行违背天性的行为，并抵御这种控制时，就可以进行一次新的豁免检定并且有+2加值。」或者欲火焚身中「目标通常不会对生物或物体产生性趣，它对抗该法术的豁免检定有+4加值。」的情况<br>可以译作：你所施展的影响心灵法术，如果在通常情况由于违背目标天性的行为而获得额外豁免机会或加值，只要行动意图为淫秽或丧心病狂（比如让德鲁伊对她的动物伙伴发情，或者兄妹互相产生欲望），目标则无法获得这加值或豁免机会。<br><br>In addition, three times per day, you can cast quickened unnatural lust as a spell-like ability.<br>此外，你每天可以作为类法术能力<del>迅捷施法三次欲火焚身（unnatural lust）。</del><br>每天3次作为类法术能力施放瞬发火焚身（quickened unnatural lust）。<br>quickened是法术瞬发法超魔（Quicken Spell）<br><br><br>Unlike with the spell, you are not limited to existing forms; you could turn the target into a three-headed nymph or a centaur-like creature made only of human body parts, for example (although this does not apply to inanimate forms, such as turning a human into a sculpture of soft clay or vice versa). <br>与该法术不同的是，你并不局限于已有的生物，例如可以将目标变成有三个头的<del>仙女</del>，或一个仅由人体组成的半人马状生物（尽管这不适用于无生命的物体，你无法把人变成软泥的雕塑，或把雕塑变成人）。<br>Nymph一般译作宁芙（Nymph）<br><br>If the resulting form would be lethal, the target gains a +4 bonus on the save. <br>如果所产生的形态是致命的，<del>那么目标会获得+4豁免奖励。</del><br>目标在此次豁免获得+4加值。<br><br>Unlike for a normal polymorph any object spell, changes you make this way can be undone only by a wish or miracle spell or by another use of this ability.<br>与普通的变形万物法术不同，你通过这种方式制造变形只能通过许愿术、<del>神力干涉</del>、或者另一次该能力来撤销。<br>你都知道wish是许愿术了，那miracle当然是神迹术啊<br><br>2: Violent Vice (Ex)<br>第二神恩 暴力罪行（Violent Vice Ex)<br>Violent Vice可以译作暴力恶癖<br><br>These temporary hit points stack with multiple uses of this ability (but not with temporary hit points from other sources), <br>这些临时生命值会因多次使用该<del>技能</del>而叠加（但不会与其他来源的临时生命值叠加），<br>ability一般是能力，skill才译作技能<br><br>As long as you are fully healed and have at least one of these temporary hit points, you gain a +4 morale bonus on attack rolls and Will saving throws.<br>只要你生命值全满并且至少有<del>一点临时生命值</del>，你在攻击骰和意志豁免上获得+4士气加值。<br>1点这样的临时生命值 <br>是什么临时生命值很重要<br><br>Your physical appearance becomes darkly beautiful and sexually appealing,<br>你的外貌变得黯淡无光而性感，<br>darkly beautiful译成黯淡无光也太惨了，我建议是「你的外观变为阴森情调的美貌」（或者直接叫哥特风？<br><br><del>传音者神恩的法术是命令术command不是谋杀指令<br>&nbsp;艳俗劝说指的是违反天性，详看支配人类<br>Mind-affecting spells you cast that would normally grant an additional saving throw or a bonus on saving throws for opposing the target’s nature do not grant these bonuses or saves, as long as the intended course of action is lurid or perverse (such as causing a druid to lust after her animal companion, or a brother and sister to lust after one another). <br><br>能以类法术能力放三次迅发欲火焚身quickened unnatural lust<br><br>在上班错太多没空对了，一会下班再说</del></div>
</div>
</div>
